
sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Main
    participant C as Chalkboard
    participant D as Drawing
    participant S as Saving
    M->>C: create_chalkboard()
    C->>D: draw()
    C->>D: erase()
    C->>S: save()
    C->>S: load()
    D-->>C: return drawing
    S-->>C: return saved work
    C-->>M: return chalkboard
